  "sections": {
    "Description": "Alpha Leapers jump to their destination and avoid all obstacles in the way. After they move they will web an adjacent target and prepare to stab it during the enemy turn for 5 damage.\nLeapers cannot spawn alongside theScorpion.",
    "Strategy": "Strategy is identical to the standardLeaper, except that its 3 health makes it more dangerous in the early phase of the game with less powerful Mechs in play. If there is an Alpha Leaper first in the attack order, look for situations where it can be displaced in such a way to hit other enemy Vek; with very high damage output of 5, the Alpha Leapers attack is strong enough to kill every non-Leader enemy."
  },
  "full_text": "Alpha Leaper\nDetails\nHealth\n3\nMove\n4\nSystems\nSharpened Fangs\n(\nEnemy\n)\nEffect\nWeb a target, preparing to stab it for 5 damage.\nAlpha Leaper\nis one of the Alpha\nVek\nfrom\nInto The Breach\n.\nDescription\n[\n]\nAlpha Leapers jump to their destination and avoid all obstacles in the way. After they move they will web an adjacent target and prepare to stab it during the enemy turn for 5 damage.\nLeapers cannot spawn alongside the\nScorpion\n.\nStrategy\n[\n]\nStrategy is identical to the standard\nLeaper\n, except that its 3 health makes it more dangerous in the early phase of the game with less powerful Mechs in play. If there is an Alpha Leaper first in the attack order, look for situations where it can be displaced in such a way to hit other enemy Vek; with very high damage output of 5, the Alpha Leapers attack is strong enough to kill every non-Leader enemy.\nv\n·\nd\n·\ne\nVek\nVek\nBeetle\n•\nBlobber\n•\nBurrower\n•\nCentipede\n•\nCrab\n•\nDigger\n•\nFirefly\n•\nHornet\n•\nLeaper\n•\nScarab\n•\nScorpion\n•\nSpider\n•\nVolatile Vek\nVek (Advanced Edition)\nBouncer\n•\nGastropod\n•\nMosquito\n•\nMoth\n•\nPlasmodia\n•\nStarfish\n•\nTumblebug\nAlpha Vek\nAlpha Beetle\n•\nAlpha Blobber\n•\nAlpha Burrower\n•\nAlpha Centipede\n•\nAlpha Crab\n•\nAlpha Digger\n•\nAlpha Firefly\n•\nAlpha Hornet\n•\nAlpha Leaper\n•\nAlpha Scarab\n•\nAlpha Scorpion\n•\nAlpha Spider\nAlpha Vek (Advanced Edition)\nAlpha Bouncer\n•\nAlpha Gastropod\n•\nAlpha Mosquito\n•\nAlpha Moth\n•\nAlpha Plasmodia\n•\nAlpha Starfish\n•\nAlpha Tumblebug\nVek Psions\nBlast Psion\n•\nBlood Psion\n•\nShell Psion\n•\nSoldier Psion\nVek Psions (Advanced Edition)\nArachnid Psion\n•\nRaging Psion\n•\nSmoldering Psion\nVek Minions\nBlob\n•\nAlpha Blob\n•\nSpiderling Egg\n•\nSpiderling\n•\nAlpha Spiderling\nVek Minions (Advanced Edition)\nSpore\n•\nAlpha Spore\n•\nVicious Spore\n•\nBlob Leader\nVek Leaders\nBeetle Leader\n•\nFirefly Leader\n•\nHornet Leader\n•\nLarge Goo\n(\nMedium Goo\n